summary: Once upon a time, I drew Tyler Posey. Or was it Scott McCall? They are so similar in temperament I guess you could see it either...
caption:
Once upon a time, I drew Tyler Posey. Or was it Scott McCall? They are so similar in temperament I guess you could see it either way.  

2 years (well a little more than that if we’re getting technical, I posted it in Feb of 2016) and still makes me smile. 

If it looks familiar to you, I originally posted this on my embarrassingly defunct side art tumblr lol. We don’t speak about it.

IG
